Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:34.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
