Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:43.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:50.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:55.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:10.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:15.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:25.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:29.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:37.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:44.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
